dialogue.introduction: Battleship Nagato class's 2nd ship, Mutsu. Pleased to meet you. Don't play with fire too much, okay? Please...
dialogue.library_intro: Battleship Nagato class's second ship and from there (referring to her name), Mutsu. Of course, I'm part of the world's Big 7. Ehh? The gunpowder explosion accident? Well, can't cover it up anymore right? This time will be fine!
dialogue.secretary3: Like I said, I told you to stop playing with fire inside me! Hey, are you listening?
dialogue.secretaryidle: Oh my, oh my oh my. Leaving Mutsu all alone over here... Oh my, oh my, oh my!
dialogue.secretarymarried: For you, I'll do my best today as well, okay?
dialogue.wedding: Admiral, why are you looking at my third gun turret? If you're going to look, look over here.
dialogue.show_players_score: There's a message for you, Admiral.
dialogue.equipment1: Oh my, it's fine. It's not like we're going to encounter anything.
dialogue.equipment3: Oh my, oh my oh my
dialogue.expedition_selection: Oh my, oh my oh my
dialogue.resource_collection: Oh my, oh my oh my
dialogue.instant_repair: Oh my, oh my oh my
dialogue.development: Oh my, oh my oh my
dialogue.docking_minor_damage: I'll be fixing my make-up for a bit.
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: My clothes have been damaged. Please treat it carefully, okay?
dialogue.docking_complete: I wonder if the repair have been completed
dialogue.ship_construction: It seems like a new warship has finished constructing.
dialogue.start_a_sortie: It's my turn huh. Okay then, I'll let them have it!
dialogue.battle_start: Enemy ship in range! All guns fire!
dialogue.night_attack: No. 3 turret... what are you doing?
dialogue.artillery_spotting: No. 3 turret... what are you doing?
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: No. 3 turret... what are you doing?
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: No. 3 turret... what are you doing?
dialogue.mvp: Oh my, me? Hmm, so those things happen too. Don't worry about it.
dialogue.sunk: Sinking in battle... I wonder why... I'm not that frustrated.
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: Ah, Nagato? Are you going out? Take this umbrella. It's going to rain all day today.
dialogue.early_summer_2015: What is it, Nagato? Oh, beach volleyball? Alright, but, do you know the rules? ... my, my, it seems I have no choice. Leave it to me.
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: Now, the end of the year cleaning is a busy time, let's have it done as soon as possible. Fufu, Nagato, can I ask you to help too?
dialogue.new_year_2016: Happy New Year, Admiral. Pleased to be of service this year as well. Oh yeah, Please take good care of Nagato as well. You know she's kind of awkward at times, right?
